Simulation - Class in youtube
The Simulation class represents a YouTube-like simulation with users, channels, videos, and streams.
Simulation() - Constructor for class youtube.Simulation
Constructs a new Simulation object, initializes user, channel, video, stream lists and starts the simulation threads ( User and Channel have thair own tasks to do).
stopThreads() - Method in class youtube.Simulation
Stops all simulation threads by setting the stopThreads flag and interrupting each thread.
Stream - Class in youtube.classes
The Stream class represents a live stream It stores information about the stream, such as stream ID, name, description, start time, number of likes, and number of users Implements Serializable for object serialization and Watchable for watchable items.
Stream(String, ImageIcon, String, String, LocalDateTime) - Constructor for class youtube.classes.Stream
Constructs a Stream object with the specified parameters.
StreamInfo - Class in youtube
The StreamInfo class represents a graphical user interface displaying information about streams.

Subject - Interface in youtube.classes
